                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>With switch in up position measure resistance between terminals 1 and 5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>Mirror switch, 1 to 5.</para>
