                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>With switch in up position measure resistance between terminals 2 and 4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>Mirror switch, 2 to 4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry rotate="0" align="center">
                            <para>&#60;1 ohm?</para>
